rows.label: qev060606_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ugh! Why are they so STUBBORN about everything?
Duty this, mission that... *fsssh* Get over yourselves![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0002
rows.name:
Oh, heyyy! It's you! What happened to you? *fsssh*
Did you end up finding a gorkwa?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0003
rows.name:
Aw, you're the best. Now I can stop with the constant
need to devoltanize a tiny bit at a time and just take in
a truckload all at once! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0004
rows.name:
...What? You look like you just swallowed a bug.
*fsssh* Is there something on my face?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask why Orleron's manner of speaking has changed.

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0020
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0021
rows.name: Express concern about Orleron fighting with Trachlo.

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0005
rows.name:
Of course it's changed! *fsssh*
While you were off getting that gorkwa, I grew up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0006
rows.name:
Ha! Pick your jaw up off the floor there. *fsssh*
Zaruboggan grow out of the rugrat phase a lot quicker
than you humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0007
rows.name:
I spent time hanging around New LA like you said.
Grew up talking to all sorts of people. *fsssh*
Guess this is how I turned out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0008
rows.name:
To hear it from Trachlo, I'm some kind of heretical
monster, but I like myself just fine. Yessir! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0009
rows.name:
And I mean, if my kind's gonna keep living with all of
you in this big city, we've got to evolve, you know?
*fsssh* Can't let the old ways keep us tied down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0010
rows.name:
I just wish Trachlo and the others would catch on to
that. Buncha old farts... *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0011
rows.name:
Like lately, they won't shut up about how I'm an affront
to Golbogga, or how I'm making light of the whole
devoltanizing thing, or...whatever. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0012
rows.name:
Aw, you worried about me? That's sweet. *fsssh*
Too bad you're about the only one...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0013
rows.name:
It's more than just Trachlo that's been chewing my metal
ass out lately. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0014
rows.name:
It's all the other Zaruboggan too. *fsssh* They won't
shut up about how I'm an affront to Golbogga, or
how I make light of the whole devoltanizing thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0015
rows.name:
*fsssh* They treat me like this huge disappointment.
Like I'm a burden on them. But everybody's got
different priorities, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0016
rows.name:
And Arsenican's basically my dad, right? *fsssh*
But now when I talk to him he's all distant,
and you can tell he's looking for an excuse to bail.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0030
rows.name: Sympathize

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0031
rows.name: Express pity for Orleron's situation.

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0040
rows.name: Criticize

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0041
rows.name: Lecture Orleron for his lifestyle.

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0017
rows.name: RIGHT?! I knew you'd get it! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0018
rows.name:
I mean, I guess he's going off a Zaruboggan mind-set.
*fsssh* They don't really do the whole parent-kid thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0019
rows.name: But like, that's no reason to outright shun me, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0020
rows.name:
Ugh, thanks a lot. Would it be the end of the world if
SOMEone sided with me for once? *fsssssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0021
rows.name:
I mean, look, I'm still a Zaruboggan, right? *fsssh*
I can imagine what about me rubs them all the wrong
way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0022
rows.name: But is that really a reason to outright shun me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0023
rows.name:
*fsssh* For my part, I still like them. All of them!
They're all good guys. But then to hear them tell me
they don't think of me as one of their own...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0024
rows.name:
...I mean, what am I supposed to do? *fsssh*
Hell, what would YOU do in my shoes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0050
rows.name: Help

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0051
rows.name: Suggest that Orleron try acting like they want him to.

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0060
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0061
rows.name:
Tell Orleron that he needs to
find that answer for himself.

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0025
rows.name: How Trachlo and the others...want me to? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0026
rows.name: Hmmm, maybe...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0027
rows.name:
Yeah, I guess that's fair. *fsssh* Gotta figure out the
really important stuff for yourself, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0028
rows.name:
Otherwise I'd be no different than them blindly clinging
to what Golbogga ordered them to do. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0029
rows.name: Hmm, maybe...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0030
rows.name:
*fsssh* I still don't buy into the whole "sacred duty"
thing, but I could stand to get more serious about the
whole devoltanizing deal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0031
rows.name:
Actually, could you do me a solid? There's supposed
to be this super polluted spot in Cauldros. *fsssh*
Think you could take me there?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0032
rows.name:
If I go there and devoltanize the lot of it, I can shove
that right in Trachlo and the others' big fat faces!
*fsssh* ...In a nice way, I mean.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0033
rows.name:
And I promise I'll pay you back for the escort,
AND for getting me this gorkwa. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0034
rows.name:
Please? It just doesn't feel right to leave things like this
with them. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0035
rows.name:
Whoooa, this has GOT to be the place! ...Heh. *fsssh*
Guess I really am a Zaruboggan after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0036
rows.name:
The sight of this much voltant has my whole body
throbbing! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0037
rows.name:
All right. *fsssh* Time to devoltanize this bad mother
with the gorkwa you found me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0038
rows.name:
Whooooa, here it comes! I can feel it like...like a wave!
*fsssh* Washing over me! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0039
rows.name:
AaaaaAAAAAAAAAAAAAH! Graah, praise Golbogga!
*fsssh* *fsssh* *fsssh* *fsssh* *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0040
rows.name:
*fsssssssssh* That...was amazing... This voltant is...wow.
Just wow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0041
rows.name:
There was no way to devoltanize all of it at once,
but I feel like I made a dent. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0042
rows.name:
That should earn me some Zaruboggan points with the
guys, right? I mean, I purified the impure. *fsssh*
That's their whole deal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0070
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0071
rows.name: Assure Orleron that he fulfilled his duty.

rows.label: qev060606_JNK0080
rows.name: Shrug

rows.label: qev060606_SEL0081
rows.name: Confess that you don't really understand any of this.

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0043
rows.name: Thanks! *fsssh* Hearing that from you really helps.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0044
rows.name: Now to go tell Trachlo all about it! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0045
rows.name:
Hmmmm... Well, I guess for you humans,
it'd be like finding the Lifehold. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0046
rows.name:
But what matters here is that Trachlo will get it. *fsssh*
Time to go report in![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0047
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0048
rows.name: Orleron, is that you? *fsssh* What is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0049
rows.name:
Hey, Trachlo! I just devoltanized that contamination
zone in Cauldros that everyone's been talking about.
*fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0050
rows.name:
Pretty sweet, huh? *fsssh* Sooooo, does that prove I'm
a real Zaruboggan or what?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0051
rows.name:
*fsssh* Cauldros?! How could you go somewhere so
dangerous—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0052
rows.name:
Relax! [ST:playername ] was with me. *fsssh*
So don't leave me hanging.
Am I back in the club or what?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0053
rows.name: You went there just to prove that? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0054
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0055
rows.name:
*fsssh* I am sure Golbogga smiles down upon your
bravery and dedication.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0056
rows.name:
Now get back to New LA immediately. *fsssh*
We cannot afford to lose a precious member of our
mission now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0057
rows.name:
You got it, boss! *fsssh* I'll bring home a family-size
helping of this voltant as a souvenir![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0058
rows.name: He finally acknowledged me, thanks to you. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev000601_JNK0090
rows.name: Encourage

rows.label: qev000601_SEL0091
rows.name: Tell Orleron to keep working hard for the cause.

rows.label: qev000601_JNK0100
rows.name: Warn

rows.label: qev000601_SEL0101
rows.name: Tell Orleron to be extra careful handling that "souvenir."

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0059
rows.name:
*fsssh* Yeah, but I'm not giving up on living free like a
human, either. I'll work...hard-ish at it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0060
rows.name:
*fsssh* Oh, that's right. This stuff's super poisonous
to you guys, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0061
rows.name:
Nah, don't worry. I love humans! *fsssh*
I'd never do anything stupid to hurt you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060606_MSG0062
rows.name:
All right, I'm heading back. Got a big fat takeout
order of voltant to deliver to the guys! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
